summary: A racemenu preset of Yennefer from the witcher 3 wild hunt.
descriptionHtml:
Took me a whole day to create her, and I think she came out pretty nice so I decided to share it on the nexus.
She is a ningheim race. Sorry I tried with the default races but I just couldn't get it right.

[b][size=3]
requirements[/size][/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?]CBBE Body[/url]   (not 100% sure if this is needed, I think you should be fine with UNP or default body too)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35474/?]Ningheim Race[/url]  (<<Very important MUST download)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Complexion[/url] (Must have if you want the same result as the screenshots)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?tab=1&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmoddescription%2F%3Fid%3D10168%26preview%3D&pUp=1]ApachiiSKYHair V1.6 Full[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33526/?]ShowRaceMenu Precache Killer[/url]  (Download this if you want to change appearance mid game. It prevents skyrim from crashing when using ''showracemenu'' command)


[b][size=3]
Installation
[/size][/b][b]Default or NMM[/b]
-Copy ''Yennefer.jslot''
-Paste it in - Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets

[b]Mod Organizer[/b]
-Copy ''Yennefer.jslot''
-Paste it in - Mod Organizer\overwrite\skse\plugins\CharGen\Presets

[b][size=3]Use ingame
[/size][/b]-Start a new game OR type ''showracemenu'' in console (without brackets)
-Once in racemenu, navigate to the preset tab on the top right.
-Hit F9 or click on load preset.
-Select Yennefer
